{"_id":"686Egcjcxa3cs8tD","name":"Militiaman","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>They pay you to keep the peace, which mainly involves looking dangerous and unapproachable. You can handle yourself in a fight though, and have the scars to prove it. You're on the side of good, whatever that means. Usually it means the man who pays the wages.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A pole-arm, a crossbow, a quiver of bolts, chain suit (light armour), a book of ordinances, and a seal of authority to show off when you need to.</p>\n<p><strong>Where have you worked? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The docks, full of foreigners.</li>\n<li>Temple district, surprisingly rough.</li>\n<li>The walls, watching for Unmen.</li>\n<li>The town square, mostly at hangings.</li>\n<li>The market, rife with robbers.</li>\n<li>The guardhouse, full of violent men.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you seen? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The crowd crush a fallen man.</li>\n<li>A child stabbed for stealing an apple.</li>\n<li>The mayor pelted with rotten fruit.</li>\n<li>A dead man, strung up by his guts.</li>\n<li>Robbers having their fingers cut off.</li>\n<li>A priest smash a rival with a sceptre.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pilot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ship gunner":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small arms":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Warp focus":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Zero G":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6ieF1OBMScWea46N","name":"Tomb Robber","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>If fools bury their dead with coin and gold, that's their problem. You just make sure all that wealth doesn't go to waste laying in some tomb. After all, who needs gold in the afterlife? You can't buy your way to the Golden Land can you, the gods judge not on material wealth but on the gold in your soul. Your soul's not worth much, so no reason to stop what you're doing.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A crowbar and medal pegs, plus a hammer and chisel; the tools of business. A thick cloak with a hood and a lantern. A club for when things go wrong.</p>\n<p><strong>What have you robbed? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>A traitor knight's tomb, newly built.</li>\n<li>The tomb of family Cesst, shattered.</li>\n<li>The crypts under Gellen cathedral.</li>\n<li>The Red King's tomb, supposedly.</li>\n<li>An elven tomb, frankly terrifying.</li>\n<li>A dwarven tomb, well constructed.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What did you find? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Gold stained red with blood.</li>\n<li>A book of blasphemy, which you kept.</li>\n<li>Nothing but death and dust.</li>\n<li>Old swords, notched and worn.</li>\n<li>The body of a ghoul, fat and swollen.</li>\n<li>Nothing but ghosts.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pilot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ship gunner":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small arms":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Warp focus":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Zero G":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9yK5qV4Hvl2umCGZ","name":"Soldier","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You've marched the Great Road, seen action against the traitor, and paraded in your best armour, such that it was. You've seen things and lived at the sharp end, which has made you hollow-eyed and jaded. Perhaps you'll get out of this way of life, but it is really all you know. Perhaps you're here for good, or at least until your luck runs out.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A bow and quiver of arrows and an arming sword, all well looked after. A shield with the emblem of your last commission and a good suit of mail (modest armour). A book of prayers to the gods, any gods.</p>\n<p><strong>Where have you served? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Pomperburg, against the traitor.</li>\n<li>The personal army of Lord Cesst.</li>\n<li>The war against Far Hissain.</li>\n<li>Against Fizzen's Freebooters.</li>\n<li>Against the goblins of Kelpernan.</li>\n<li>The Black Road war, very bad.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you seen? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Wizards burning men for the traitor.</li>\n<li>Goblins eat the dead.</li>\n<li>Unmen squeal as you cut them down.</li>\n<li>Deserters hung by the dozen.</li>\n<li>A troll kill ten before it fell!</li>\n<li>A village burned; the peasants killed.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pilot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ship gunner":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small arms":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Warp focus":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Zero G":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CS6VYDCUCos3ajqP","name":"Entertainer","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You can hold a tune, play an instrument or tell a story, good enough that others will listen. People like you for that reason, and listen to what you have to say. Not that you take advantage of that. Not at all. But hey, everyone has to make a living right? Nothing wrong with telling people what they want to hear, and if it helps you, that's just a coincidence, right?</p>\n<p>Equipment: A musical instrument or book of stories, a dagger, nice clothes and a jaunty hat that marks you as someone to watch. A roll of parchment with that play you've been working on.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you have entertained? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The crowds outside the grand temple.</li>\n<li>The patrons of the Broken Swan.</li>\n<li>The royal opera house.</li>\n<li>Lady Polbeck's last and greatest party.</li>\n<li>The beggars, you feel sorry for them.</li>\n<li>Anyone who'll listen on the streets.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you learned? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The mayor loves to sing.</li>\n<li>Holbrick is a swindler.</li>\n<li>Great stories are often unappreciated.</li>\n<li>Poetry is not for you.</li>\n<li>Sweet words hide ugly thoughts.</li>\n<li>There's money in well-spoken lies.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSki