{"_id":"GcbTiaCDygX9IUwW","name":"Beggar","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Seated by the side of the road, you're ignored by almost everyone - they don't even notice you are there. Which doesn't help you eat, but does mean you tend to see things others might prefer to go unnoticed. You can spot a soft touch in the crowd, and when things are tight and you need some help, you also know people - not good people, but useful people.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A wooden club for defence, ragged clothes, a messy bedroll. A bottle of something that helps you forget how hard the floor is.</p>\n<p><strong>What you've seen (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Things coming out of the sewers.</li>\n<li>What the Mayor gets up to.</li>\n<li>Where the pickpockets live.</li>\n<li>The secret of Madam von Hossburg.</li>\n<li>A murder, silent and beautiful.</li>\n<li>A person supposed to be dead.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who you know (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The captain of the Peacock Guard.</li>\n<li>The silent priest of the Red King.</li>\n<li>Silias, the silver thief.</li>\n<li>The beautiful charlatan Mimirik.</li>\n<li>The Dark Man and his bitter gang.</li>\n<li>You don't know anyone, honest.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLeve