{"_id":"HbBPJnBAGrY89BlM","name":"Grave Robber","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Certainly not how you imagined your life going, but sometimes you have to do what fate decided. For some reason certain people want bodies, and someone's got to supply them. You have no problem staring the recently dead in the face, so long as it puts food on the table and clothes on your back. The smell is bad though, hard to get rid of, and people often seem to avoid you. Ah well.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A dagger, a pony, a shovel and a bag for the body, the tools of you trade. An icon of a saint, who you secretly beg for mercy.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you have you dug up? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Your mother - a sad day.</li>\n<li>An elven prince, bedecked in garlands.</li>\n<li>The last king of a forgotten land.</li>\n<li>The buried silver of the Merchant Hess.</li>\n<li>The thigh of saint Asxe, holy relic.</li>\n<li>A traitor wrongly hanged as a wizard.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who seeks you, perhaps beyond death? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The pale shade of Prince Sargelo.</li>\n<li>The von Hocken family, beset with grief.</li>\n<li>Your lover, who you buried and robbed.</li>\n<li>The soul of a Fire priest, burning.</li>\n<li>Your partner, betrayed.</li>\n<li>No one. As far as you know...</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pilot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ship gunner":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small arms":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Warp focus":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Zero G":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KM9f9XZsWZ8gjh1i","name":"Bounty Hunter","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You keep to yourself. Your face is enough to keep most people away. You have a knack for finding people, people that don't want to be found. Mainly that's a result of knowing the right people - or the wrong people, as most would see it. But you're handy with a blade too, as most of the people you are looking for will do a lot not to get found.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A dagger, chain and leather (modest armour), a crossbow. A roll of parchment showing faces and names for you to look out for.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you have caught? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The murderer of Madam Von Hock.</li>\n<li>The Tresselback arsonist.</li>\n<li>Your sister. Don't ask.</li>\n<li>Deserters from the royal army.</li>\n<li>The wrong person, but don't tell.</li>\n<li>The agitator Hemlock.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who you're searching for? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The halfling poisoner Rubis.</li>\n<li>The lover of Jizt, a jilted noble.</li>\n<li>Horse thieves from Pure Ballalas.</li>\n<li>The heretical priest Kinns.</li>\n<li>A reason to hope, in a dark land.</li>\n<li>A way out and into the light.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCare