{"_id":"L6ozt8ZunJhzzzU9","name":"Outlaw","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>It's hard to make a living in the Kingdom, and they forced you to make a bad choice. Robbing is simple and straightforward. A blade is a great persuader. The difficult bit is living long enough to spend what you have - those Road Wardens are everywhere, and some people seem to frown on an honest thief's work. What is the world coming to?</p>\n<p>Equipment: A rusty arming sword, mail, leathers and a battered shield (light armour). A facemask. A letter from a victim to their lover, too poetic to discard.</p>\n<p><strong>What did you do? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Refused to pay the tithe on your crops.</li>\n<li>Threw rotten vegetables at the mayor.</li>\n<li>Stole coins from a drunk lord.</li>\n<li>Killed an artisan in a pub brawl.</li>\n<li>No idea, they wouldn't say.</li>\n<li>Handed out leaflets for the traitor.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who hunts you? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The town guard, always watchful.</li>\n<li>An outlaw captain, who hates you.</li>\n<li>Your family, eager to have you back.</li>\n<li>A priest of the Red King, for revenge.</li>\n<li>The king's army, as a recruit.</li>\n<li>The Bandit Lord, you saw his lair.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCaree