{"_id":"MN3QrxkS45fmuDbi","name":"Road Warden","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The roads are the veins of the Kingdom, and you have a simple task - keep them flowing. Goblins, unmen, bandits and other dangers threaten the flow, and you must face all. Still, your kind are woefully under-resourced and the danger grows daily, so you have to think smart if you are going to succeed. And by succeed I mean stay alive.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A horse, your best friend. A pole-arm for barring the way and a crossbow to back it up. A small tent and cooking gear for when you're on the road.</p>\n<p><strong>Where have you travelled? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The roads to the capital, well-guarded.</li>\n<li>The road to Cesst keep, dangerous.</li>\n<li>The Great Way, full of refugees.</li>\n<li>The Pomperburg road, full of deserters.</li>\n<li>The trade route to Far Hissain.</li>\n<li>The Black Road, goblin country.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you seen? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unmen in the forests, watching.</li>\n<li>A caravan caught by murderous bandits.</li>\n<li>Goblin raid on a noble's grand tour.</li>\n<li>Routers run through by the army.</li>\n<li>A dragon, flying high above luckily!</li>\n<li>A flash flood drown a merchant's van.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"