{"_id":"NlNZaAJYYD22kSIS","name":"Initiate","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The gods are many, and powerful. Their actions can be seen every day, in the miracle of life and the endless procession of the stars. Gods make the sun rise, the rivers flow and the forests teem. Your job is to remind the common folk of this and persuade them to worship. It's not easy.</p>\n<p>Equipment: Long robes of your god, a helmet and shield of your faith (light armour), a mace, a book of prayer and a single spell.</p>\n<p><strong>Who is your god? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Red King, angry and vengeful.</li>\n<li>The Thrice Blessed, noble and proud.</li>\n<li>The Wild Wood, fierce and savage.</li>\n<li>The Dragon, power incarnate.</li>\n<li>The Heartstone, solid and wise.</li>\n<li>A god only you have heard of.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What is your personal creed? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Give as you take, take what you need.</li>\n<li>Love is false, only death is absolute.</li>\n<li>Power is weakness, weakness is strength.</li>\n<li>Death is a game of chance, god's will.</li>\n<li>Wisdom is knowledge, knowledge is life.</li>\n<li>Everything is dust, except love.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSki