{"_id":"ZArO3u4k3KzN5Ujn","name":"Agitator","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You spend your time stirring things up, digging into the psyche of the mob and twisting it to your ends. You are a good speaker, good at manipulating people, and at prodding the sore spots. That grain riot in Galdenback? That was you. You had some thing to do with the burning of the warehouse on the shores of the river Eld, some say. You don't comment.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A notched and nasty dagger, a leather jerkin (light armour), pamphlets, seditious writings. A bottle of grog that could be set on fire, you know, if you had to.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you've worked for (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Heldehall crime gang.</li>\n<li>Steepleman, the Mayor's rival.</li>\n<li>The cult of the Stag.</li>\n<li>The Gilvenburg trade house.</li>\n<li>Someone called The Knife.</li>\n<li>You don't know. Which is worrying.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who's hunting you? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Guard, deadly and vengeful.</li>\n<li>The Guild, bedecked with lawyers.</li>\n<li>The Church, saintly and poisonous.</li>\n<li>Your brother, hateful but sad.</li>\n<li>A goblin band, angry and mad.</li>\n<li>You don't know. Which is worrying.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}