{"_id":"aEsAhNggkAAYK8ye","name":"Hunter","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>In the wilds it is hard to survive - it's a case of eat or be eaten. You're determined to be the one who eats. Moving stealthily through the brush, you spy out your target, and then you make the kill. Hunting monsters or people isn't much different really, except they tend to complain more when you shoot them. Ah well.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A good hunting bow and a quiver of arrows, a brown and green cloak, snares and traps and cooking pots and pans. A bag of herbs, worth their weight in gold.</p>\n<p><strong>Where have you been? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Black Spine mountains, ice-bound.</li>\n<li>The forest of Helmsby, dark and old.</li>\n<li>The great river Alase, wild and dark.</li>\n<li>The caverns of Trime, cold and sad.</li>\n<li>The royal forest, full of quarry.</li>\n<li>The broken plain, blasted and dry.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you hunted? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The great deer, sacred to elves.</li>\n<li>The goblins who killed your family.</li>\n<li>Trolls, fat with hate.</li>\n<li>A wyvern, wild and proud.</li>\n<li>The talking bears of the ancient woods.</li>\n<li>Anything that moves, you've got to eat.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerS