{"_id":"adTUxHO49jWTj9St","name":"Boatman","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Messing about on the river some call it, but in reality they know the rivers are the lifeblood of the Kingdom, and the boatmen are the true lords. Or so you say. Still, there's a lot to be learned on the river, and you certainly see some interesting places and meet some interesting people. But the boat is where you heart really lies.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A wooden club for defence, workman's cloths, a bedroll and backpack. A pack of cards for those slow nights, and a picture of a saint.</p>\n<p><strong>Where you've been (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The capital city, bedecked in flags.</li>\n<li>The badlands, rife with goblins.</li>\n<li>The great port and wine-dark sea.</li>\n<li>Lake Gossenham, and the floating fort.</li>\n<li>The bloody canals of Westerlan.</li>\n<li>The rapids of the mighty Alase river.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What you've seen (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Goblins burn a town with glee.</li>\n<li>The lair of the loved Bandit king.</li>\n<li>Blind traders from far Arais.</li>\n<li>A sea beast, deadly and beautiful.</li>\n<li>A handsome captain murdered for coin.</li>\n<li>Enough of war to last a lifetime.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pilot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ship gunner":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small arms":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Warp focus":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Zero G":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bR9YW9dgrRH3HuQ4","name":"Wizard's Apprentice","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Ah magic. The greatest power of the Kingdom. At least that's what your master said, before he kicked you out to 'see the world'. Apparently travelling the land in the company of mere mortals is good for your magical attunement, or some such. You're beginning the suspect that your master just didn't want the distraction from his very important 'research'.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A cloak with magical emblems so you look the part. A staff to aid your journey, and some books on magical theory. A backpack full of herbs and magical gewgaws. One spell of your choice.</p>\n<p><strong>Where have you been? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Pomperburg, you left in a hurry.</li>\n<li>The magical colleges in the capital.</li>\n<li>Nowhere worth your time.</li>\n<li>The forest roads, never again.</li>\n<li>The Golden Cave, magical!</li>\n<li>The passes of the Cragtop mountains.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you learned? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Wizards are better than other folk.</li>\n<li>The road is a harsh mistress.</li>\n<li>People fear magic more than the gods.</li>\n<li>Magic can't save you from a sword.</li>\n<li>Food is worth more than books!</li>\n<li>Nothing. This is pointless.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pilot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ship gunner":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small arms":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Warp focus":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Zero G":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bhWC4SyrNyMYqZu2","name":"Bodyguard","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You've guarded everyone from merchants in fear of rivals to rich nobles after some fun in the rougher parts of town. You know how to keep quiet and look mean - all you need, most of the time. But things get out of hand and you need to pull a weapon, you're ready for that too. Never lost a client. So far.</p>\n<p>Equipment: An arming sword, chain and leather with a small shield (modest armour), knuckle-dusters. A letter from your mother, which you cherish when times get hard.</p>\n<p><strong>Who you have protected? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Vilus, the vile priest.</li>\n<li>The head of the von Tassenback family.</li>\n<li>The dwarven map forger, Haddous.</li>\n<li>Lady Consetta, the sly opera singer.</li>\n<li>The crimelord Garhen the elf.</li>\n<li>Lord Fellini, a fool in disguise.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>A secret you know about them (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>They drink wine like a fish.</li>\n<li>They visit the more exotic brothels.</li>\n<li>They once killed someone, for love.</li>\n<li>Where they keep the gold.</li>\n<li>Who their late lamented mother was.</li>\n<li>Why they hate the King's guard.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":