{"_id":"dQL9v8euhzVKCicM","name":"Miner","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Holes in the ground are dangerous places, but they can be full of treasure - ores, metals... even gold. You're experienced at digging those treasures out for profit. No one says mines are pleasant places (well, the dwarves do), but you know there's money to be made in the bowels of the earth.</p>\n<p>Equipment: A pick and shovel, hardy and rough clothing, a lantern and a sack for that lovely ore. A wooden carving of a mine spirit, said to ward off others of its kind.</p>\n<p><strong>What have you dug up? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Gold, pure and simple. Men die for it.</li>\n<li>Metal ore, good for making weapons.</li>\n<li>Crystals, the wizards pay well.</li>\n<li>Nothing but dirt and ghosts.</li>\n<li>The buried treasure of a dead king.</li>\n<li>The entrance to a blackened tomb.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you seen? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Trolls nesting in great caverns.</li>\n<li>The skull of a dragon, long dead.</li>\n<li>Murder in the depths, out of sight.</li>\n<li>A goblin town, complete with brats.</li>\n<li>Ghosts drifting from the walls.</li>\n<li>A shrine to an outlawed god, deserted.</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pilot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ship gunner":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small arms":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Warp focus":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Zero G":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eZV0dRCG0ynBXkkT","name":"Rat Catcher","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>In the cities and towns, there's vermin aplenty, and people who'll pay to get rid of it. Though it might not be the nicest job, someone has to do it, and you can always sell what you catch for a few coins. People always want meat, and as an added bonus you now know the places to avoid when you're after a pie...</p>\n<p>Equipment: A ratter, a small, nasty dog. A staff festooned with dead rats, the mark of your trade. A few traps, some with live vermin. Want to buy one?</p>\n<p><strong>Where have you worked? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Grim Biskerstaf, the rotten city.</li>\n<li>The market, it's crawling with vermin.</li>\n<li>The home of Lord Cesst, surprisingly.</li>\n<li>The dockside warehouses, at night.</li>\n<li>In the sewers, I don't recommend it.</li>\n<li>Everywhere, why do you ask?</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What have you seen? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Things in the sewers, man-like things.</li>\n<li>Lord Kemp paying an assassin.</li>\n<li>A stabbing in the back alleys.</li>\n<li>A way into the palace, unguarded.</li>\n<li>The skull of a rat a foot across.</li>\n<li>The backside of life. You?</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"