{"_id":"fyuUPPf1eSIYuOfo","name":"Raconteur","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You can tell a good tale, that's for sure. Weave narrative like your life depended on it, and you have a good eye for what you audience wants to hear. Is it all true? Well, not exactly true. Like all great stories it has a life of it's own, so does that really matter? It seems to some, yes. Which is a shame, but there you go. Have I ever told you of the time I..?</p>\n<p>Equipment: Jaunty clothes, a bottle or two of something strong. An arming sword, few 'relics' of your past exploits, impressive but worthless.</p>\n<p><strong>What tales do you tell? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>War stories, from your army days.</li>\n<li>Tales of exploration in deepest Kulk.</li>\n<li>The latest tales from the capital.</li>\n<li>Gossip from the salons of the nobles.</li>\n<li>Stories of the highway men and outlaws.</li>\n<li>Stuff you read in books, all true!</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Where have you been? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The capital, where you're well-known.</li>\n<li>Where haven't you been?</li>\n<li>Fesselburg, you knew the traitor.</li>\n<li>Fair Marenesse, you served on ship.</li>\n<li>The great battle of Pomperburg!</li>\n<li>Here and there. Buy me a drink?</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":12,"isCareerSkill":true},"Survival":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Swimming":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Thrown":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false}},"warpstar":{"Animal handler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Astronav":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blades":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"