{"_id":"wCJZwUztUQtCG4HK","name":"Gambler","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>A fool and his money are soon parted. You're no fool, but the gambling pits of the Kingdom, be they back-street dens or aristocrat casinos are awash with them. You're good at finding a mark, and playing the odds in your favour so that you get what you need. And if you make a few enemies on the way, that's life huh?</p>\n<p>Equipment: A deck of cards, well-thumbed, nice clothes and a serious hat that marks you as a player. A roll of parchment with your best cheats scribbled on it.</p>\n<p><strong>Who have you fleeced? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Anise, arrogant mistress of Fulbeck.</li>\n<li>Your father. Needs must.</li>\n<li>An aspiring priest of his last coppers.</li>\n<li>The mercenary Jagar. An error.</li>\n<li>The gullible son of Lord Vech.</li>\n<li>Who haven't you fleeced?</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who wants revenge? (roll a [[/roll 1d6]])</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The casino owner, who's on to you.</li>\n<li>Your partner. Well, one-time partner.</li>\n<li>Your lover, who you gambled away.</li>\n<li>That princeling, who knows you cheat.</li>\n<li>Your father, for your dissolute ways.</li>\n<li>Who doesn't want revenge?</li>\n</ol>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":10,"isCareerSkill":true},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History